<main>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Novel Reading Tool</h2>
        <div>
            This reading tool is to enhance the user's reading experience on existing websites by providing additional features such as:
            <ul class="browser-default">
                <li><b>Dark mode</b> (this was the main reason this tool was made tbh. Google chrome plugins don't work on phones ðŸ˜¢).</li>
                <li>Highlight paragraph and <b>automatically scroll</b> at the reading speed that you choose.</li>
                <li>Highlight paragraph and use <b>text-to-speech</b> to read the text to you at the speed you choose.</li>
                <li><b>Tap to scroll</b> down a page</li>
                <li>If this is a continous reading material, it will attempt to <b>find the next page</b> for you.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p>
            Disclaimer: Please use this tool ethically, such as for public material content that are not monetized. 
            The main purpose is to give additional features to enhance the reading experience. This will not store any data it extracts. 
        </p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col s12">
                <input id="url" placeholder="URL of the website that contains the text" type="url" class="validate">
                <label for="url">Article/Text URL</label>
                <span class="helper-text" data-error="Please enter a valid URL"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col s6">
                <input id="autoscroll-read" type="checkbox"/>
                <span>Automatically scroll based on reading speed</span>
            </label>
            <div class="input-field col s6">
                <input id="words-per-minute" placeholder="270" type="number" class="validate">
                <label for="words-per-minute">Reading Speed (WPM)</label>
                <span class="helper-text" data-error="Please enter a valid number"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col s6">
                <input id="autoscroll-text-to-speech" type="checkbox"/>
                <span>Automatically scroll with text to speech</span>
            </label>
            <div class="range-field col s6">
                <label for="text-to-speech-rate">Text-to-Speech Rate</label>
                <input id="text-to-speech-rate" value="1" type="range" min="1" max="7">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <label class="col s12">
                <input id="autoload-next" type="checkbox"/>
                <span>Automatically load next page</span>
            </label>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <button id="submit" class="btn waves-effect waves-light right" type="submit" name="action">Submit
                <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>